Name: Tempo
About the game: Control Musa, the musical disco note. Travel through various surreal environments and dance across the universe! See if you can move faster than your friends and achieve the highest BPM. Tempo is a single-player rhythm game that offers an audiovisual arcade experience to test your speed and accuracy. Speedrun high-intensity levels by mastering the tracks to top the global leaderboards. Support for: -Mouse and Keyboard -Controller
